tandard issue for adventurers in the Wastes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 20.5684%;\">Rations, 1 day</td>\n<td style=\"width: 12.2828%;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 66.3859%;\">Food and Water</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 20.5684%;\">Rope, 20m</td>\n<td style=\"width: 12.2828%;\">15</td>\n<td style=\"width: 66.3859%;\">-</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 20.5684%;\">Tent</td>\n<td style=\"width: 12.2828%;\">40</td>\n<td style=\"width: 66.3859%;\">Can fit 3 comfortably, 5 uncomfortably.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 20.5684%;\">Torches (6)</td>\n<td style=\"width: 12.2828%;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 66.3859%;\">Each burns for 1 hour</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 20.5684%;\">Lighter</td>\n<td style=\"width: 12.2828%;\">10</td>\n<td style=\"width: 66.3859%;\">Throw 2D on each use; gas runs out on 4-</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>"}
